title: Jax In The Blossom Garden
body:
Just something I have made in my spare time, A peaceful yet simple picture of Jax training in a open field with a blossom tree behind him. Hope you enjoy :) 

I might do some more depending on the feedback!

*Sorry About The Blur,*

~JD

> {{champion:24}}              **"Who wants a piece of the champ?"**

replies.body: Looks amazing! You should, in my opinion, try doing Tristana and Teemo. There aren't any good pictures of them, so, it seemed like a nice project that you could do. :)
Ok Sure why not. I have some themes that I have planned for teemo!
Cheers for the positive feedback Terra!
